           <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M17 6h2a2 2 0 012 2v1a4 4 0 01-4 4M7 6H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v1a4 4 0 004 4"/>`,
