---

<Layout title="Score Padel — Plataforma Global de Pádel">
  <Navbar />
  <!-- HERO (full-bleed background image like login) -->
  <div class="relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <img
        src="/images/hero-padel.png"
        alt=""
        role="presentation"
        class="h-full w-full object-cover object-[30%_center]"
        loading="eager"
        decoding="async"
      />
    </div>
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0"
      style="background: linear-gradient(to left, rgba(14,10,6,0.95) 0%, rgba(20,14,10,0.88) 28%, rgba(40,25,15,0.55) 55%, rgba(255,186,8,0.08) 100%);"
    >
    </div>
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0"
      style="background: radial-gradient(circle at 85% 15%, rgba(255,186,8,0.12), transparent 30%);"
    >
    </div>
    <section data-scroll-reveal class="relative min-h-screen pt-24 pb-20" style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; align-items:start;">
      <div></div>
      <div class="relative z-10 pt-16 pr-8 pl-4 lg:pr-16 lg:pl-8 max-w-xl">
          <div
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-white/12 mb-6 backdrop-blur-sm"
          >
            <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#FFBA08] animate-pulse"></span>
            <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-white/80 tracking-wide uppercase"
              >Plataforma activa</span
            >
          </div>
          <h1
            class="font-display text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight leading-[1.08] mb-4 text-white"
          >
            La plataforma global<br />
            <span
              style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FFBA08 0%, #fb923c 100%); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text;"
              >del pádel amateur.</span
            >
          </h1>
          <p class="text-sm sm:text-base text-white/75 max-w-xl leading-relaxed mb-3">
            Organización, valoración y competición para jugadores de todos los niveles.
          </p>
          <p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-white/55 max-w-xl leading-relaxed mb-8">
            12 niveles y 3 divisiones basado en datos reales. Registra partidos, sigue tu evolución
            y compite en torneos.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
            <a
              href="/registro"
              class="px-7 py-3.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white rounded-full shadow-[0_20px_40px_-20px_rgba(208,79,0,0.9)] transition-transform duration-200 hover:-translate-y-0.5"
              style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e85d04 0%, #fb923c 50%, #ffba08 100%);"
            >
              Crear cuenta gratis
            </a>
            <a
              href="#como-funciona"
              class="px-7 py-3.5 border-2 border-white/20 text-white text-sm font-semibold rounded-full hover:border-white/40 hover:bg-white/8 transition-all backdrop-blur-sm"
            >
              Cómo funciona
            </a>
          </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <!-- LIVE STATS BAR -->
  <section data-scroll-reveal class="relative z-20 -mt-8 px-6 pb-10 lg:px-8">
    <div
      class="mx-auto max-w-7xl rounded-[2rem] border border-white/40 px-4 py-4 text-white shadow-[0_28px_70px_-30px_rgba(208,79,0,0.55)] sm:px-6 sm:py-6"
      style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f97316 0%, #fb923c 45%, #fdba74 100%);"
    >
      <div class="mb-4 flex justify-center sm:mb-5">
        <span
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-white/14 px-4 py-2 text-[11px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-white/80"
        >
          <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-white animate-pulse"></span>
          Estado en directo
        </span>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-center sm:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-5 sm:gap-4">
        <div class="rounded-[1.4rem] border border-white/15 bg-black/10 px-4 py-5 backdrop-blur-sm">
          <div
            class="font-display text-3xl font-extrabold text-white sm:text-4xl stat-number"
            data-target={totalPlayers}
          >
            {totalPlayers}
          </div>
          <div class="mt-1 text-xs font-medium text-white/72 sm:text-sm">Jugadores registrados</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-[1.4rem] border border-white/15 bg-black/10 px-4 py-5 backdrop-blur-sm">
          <div
            class="font-display text-3xl font-extrabold text-white sm:text-4xl stat-number"
            data-target={totalMatches}
          >
            {totalMatches}
          </div>
          <div class="mt-1 text-xs font-medium text-white/72 sm:text-sm">Partidos jugados</div>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-[1.4rem] border border-white/15 bg-black/10 px-4 py-5 backdrop-blur-sm">
          <div
            class="font-display text-3xl font-extrabold text-white sm:text-4xl stat-number"
            data-target={totalTournaments}
          >
            {totalTournaments}
          </div>
          <div class="mt-1 text-xs font-medium text-white/72 sm:text-sm">Torneos creados</div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="rounded-[1.4rem] border border-white/15 bg-black/10 px-4 py-5 backdrop-blur-sm relative overflow-hidden"
        >
          <div class="absolute top-2 right-2">
            <span
              class="inline-flex items-center px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-white/20 text-[9px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider"
              >Semanal</span
            >
          </div>
          <div
            class="font-display text-3xl font-extrabold text-white sm:text-4xl stat-number"
            data-target={weeklyNewPlayers}
          >
            +{weeklyNewPlayers}
          </div>
          <div class="mt-1 text-xs font-medium text-white/72 sm:text-sm">Nuevos jugadores</div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="rounded-[1.4rem] border border-white/15 bg-black/10 px-4 py-5 backdrop-blur-sm col-span-2 sm:col-span-1 relative overflow-hidden"
        >
          <div class="absolute top-2 right-2">
            <span
              class="inline-flex items-center px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-white/20 text-[9px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider"
              >Semanal</span
            >
          </div>
          <div
            class="font-display text-3xl font-extrabold text-white sm:text-4xl stat-number"
            data-target={weeklyMatches}
          >
            +{weeklyMatches}
          </div>
          <div class="mt-1 text-xs font-medium text-white/72 sm:text-sm">Partidos esta semana</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TOP 10 DESTACADOS -->
  <section data-scroll-reveal id="destacados" class="py-24 section-light">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-5 gap-12 items-start">
        <div class="lg:col-span-2">
          <span
            class="inline-block text-xs font-bold text-coral uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-4 bg-coral/10 px-3 py-1 rounded-full"
            >Destacados</span
          >
          <h2
            class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-4 text-navy"
          >
            Top 10 jugadores
          </h2>
          <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Los jugadores con mayor valoración en la plataforma. Tu nombre podría estar aquí.
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-muted">
            <svg
              class="w-4 h-4 text-teal"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6"></path>
            </svg>
            Actualizado en tiempo real tras cada partido
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-3">
          {
            topRanking.length > 0 ? (
              <div class="space-y-2">
                {topRanking.map((player: any, i: number) => (
                  <div
                    class={`card-hover p-4 flex items-center gap-4 ${i < 3 ? 'border-l-3 border-l-coral' : ''}`}
                  >
                    <div
                      class={`w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 font-display font-extrabold text-sm ${i === 0 ? 'bg-amber/20 text-amber' : i === 1 ? 'bg-gray-200 text-gray-500' : i === 2 ? 'bg-orange-100 text-orange-400' : 'bg-gray-50 text-gray-400'}`}
                    >
                      {i + 1}
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
                      <div class="text-sm font-bold text-navy truncate">{player.name}</div>
                      <div class="text-[11px] text-muted truncate">
                        {player.location || 'Sin ubicación'} · {player.matches_played} partidos
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="shrink-0 text-right">
                      <div class="font-display text-lg font-extrabold text-coral">
                        {Number(player.rating).toFixed(1)}
                      </div>
                      <div class="text-[10px] text-muted uppercase tracking-wide">valoración</div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                ))}
              </div>
            ) : (
              <div class="card p-10 text-center">
                <p class="text-sm text-muted">Aún no hay jugadores con partidos registrados.</p>
                <a
                  href="/registro"
                  class="mt-3 inline-flex text-sm font-semibold text-coral hover:underline"
                >
                  Sé el primero →
                </a>
              </div>
            )
          }
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="deep-zone">
    <!-- QUIÉNES SOMOS -->
    <section data-scroll-reveal id="quienes-somos" class="py-24 bg-[#2D2A26]">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
          <div>
            <span
              class="inline-block text-xs font-bold text-coral uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-4 bg-coral/10 px-3 py-1 rounded-full"
              >Quiénes somos</span
            >
            <h2
              class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-8 text-navy"
            >
              Transformando la escena<br />del pádel mundial
            </h2>
            <div class="space-y-5 text-muted leading-relaxed">
              <p>
                Score Padel es <span class="text-navy font-medium"
                  >la respuesta a la necesidad de transformar la escena del pádel</span
                >. Nacimos con el propósito de organizar y estandarizar las competiciones,
                jerarquizar a los jugadores y proporcionar una plataforma global donde cada
                deportista cuente su propia historia de éxito.
              </p>
              <p>
                Somos el impulso que eleva el pádel, ofreciendo <span class="text-navy font-medium"
                  >orden, sentido y comunidad</span
                > a la escena amateur y profesional apasionada por este deporte.
              </p>
              <p>
                Nuestra misión trasciende el simple juego: <span class="text-navy font-medium"
                  >empoderamos a cada jugador</span
                > brindándole la oportunidad de identificarse en su nivel y trazar sus propios caminos
                de progreso en cada evento, con visibilidad internacional.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="card p-8 space-y-6">
              <!-- Padel racket icon: valoración objetiva -->
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div
                  class="w-11 h-11 rounded-xl bg-coral/10 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0"
                >
                  <svg
                    class="w-6 h-6 text-coral"
                    viewBox="0 0 28 40"
                    fill="none"
                    aria-hidden="true"
                  >
                    <rect x="11" y="29" width="6" height="10" rx="3" fill="currentColor"></rect>
                    <line
                      x1="11.5"
                      y1="31.5"
                      x2="16.5"
                      y2="31.5"
                      stroke="white"
                      stroke-width="0.9"
                      opacity="0.4"></line>
                    <line
                      x1="11.5"
                      y1="34"
                      x2="16.5"
                      y2="34"
                      stroke="white"
                      stroke-width="0.9"
                      opacity="0.4"></line>
                    <line
                      x1="11.5"
                      y1="36.5"
                      x2="16.5"
                      y2="36.5"
                      stroke="white"
                      stroke-width="0.9"
